{"tid":640414,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有隻雀仔困住左，出唔返去","createTime":"2018-04-24T09:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T10:52:45.000Z","uid":72240,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8f3965827b234c2d5b55fc2f424fe108566955","tid":640414,"uid":72240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:13:45.000Z","msg":"稅務局4樓有隻雀仔飛咗入嚟，但飛唔返出去<br />\n<br />\n聽個姐姐遠講已經飛左成朝 <br />\n<br />\n有嘗試過用外套睇下可唔可以包住佢 帶佢走<br />\n<br />\n但佢太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  根本捉唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你班垃圾保安，叫你幫幫手一齊帶佢走 扮撚哂唔識聽廣東話 凈係識禁電話，叫我去櫃台問 我唔撚係問稅局野呀<br />\n<br />\n漁農署打極電話都係話跟進緊，我係稅局逗留左三個鐘 文件都整好 最後人影都無隻<br />\n<br />\n其他人凈係識講有雀仔入左黎 好慘呀 一啲行動都無<br />\n<br />\n好無助 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/24/171231_d9ecf16a3cd20cb90c4f396127ac229a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2F171231_d9ecf16a3cd20cb90c4f396127ac229a.png&h=ec1e312f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有幫手個位年輕人，你有睇連登既話 我想講聲唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef245d9cb12215fdc0cb972d78df17bcabc94c20","tid":640414,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"放d包引佢啦"},{"pid":"c0d405763722a0fa6fc5f1dc7fa7382dc0de25e5","tid":640414,"uid":72240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef245d9cb12215fdc0cb972d78df17bcabc94c20","tid":640414,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:16:38.000Z","msg":"放d包引佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"個一下諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0de81111adbffcf7b7207d0d86cde8ca43e4ee","tid":640414,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T09:24:25.000Z","msg":"咁宜家點"},{"pid":"5180a5323bbcd2abdd34d6a69c4dd1fa2